          "ModRequired": null
        },
        {
          "Text": "Equip the Wishbone from Bonemass in high-altitude areas — it pings and sparks when you are above a Silver Vein",
          "Category": "gathering",
          "ModRequired": null
        },
        {
          "Text": "Onion Seeds are found in chests inside ruined stone cabins — grow them for Onion Soup, a cheap stamina food",
